      "damage_multiplier": 1.0,
      "effects": [
        {
          "name": "damage",
          "params": {
            "magnitude": 841,
            "element": "physical"
          }
        }
      ],
      "flavor_text": "The weight of flooded tunnels finds its answer in a single, decisive blow. What the water loosened, the strike finishes."
    },
    {
      "id": "skill_000959",
      "name": "Pickfall Seam Pressure",
      "role": "sustain",
      "canonical_element": "physical",
      "seasonal_element": null,
      "geometry_type": "single_target",
      "energy_cost": 26.6,
      "cooldown_seconds": 7.8,
      "damage_multiplier": 1.0,
      "effects": [
        {
          "name": "heal",
          "params": {
            "magnitude": 1682
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "heal_over_time",
          "params": {
            "tick_heal": 505,
            "duration_seconds": 6.8
          }
        }
      ],
      "flavor_text": "Where the pick once rang and the walls held fast, a slow weight settles into the wound \u2014 not crushing, but filling, the way deep water finds every crack. The stillness of stone remembers how to carry."
    },
    {
      "id": "skill_000809",
      "name": "Pickfall Seam Pressure",
      "role": "damage_over_time",
      "canonical_element": "physical",
      "seasonal_element": null,
      "geometry_type": "melee_strike",
      "energy_cost": 19.8,
      "cooldown_seconds": 4.8,
      "damage_multiplier": 1.0,
      "effects": [
        {
          "name": "bleed",
          "params": {
            "tick_damage": 1009,
            "duration_seconds": 4.3
          }
        }
      ],
      "flavor_text": "Something deep in the rock remembers the weight of the pick, and the wound opens along that old memory. It bleeds the way a seam bleeds \u2014 slow, persistent, following the grain."
    },
    {
      "id": "skill_000810",
      "name": "Pickfall Roll",
      "role": "mobility",
      "canonical_element": "physical",
      "seasonal_element": null,
      "geometry_type": "dash_attack",
      "energy_cost": 15.6,
      "cooldown_seconds": 7.7,
      "damage_multiplier": 1.0,
      "effects": [
        {
          "name": "buff_dodge",
          "params": {
            "percent": 0.31,
            "duration_seconds": 8.4
          }
        }
      ],
      "flavor_text": "The dwarf reads the shaft before it reads them \u2014 a sudden drop into the tunnel's hollow dark, carried by the same momentum that once shook ore loose from the seam. The body learns to fall like water finds its level, fast and without argument."
    },
    {
      "id": "skill_000811",
      "name": "Pickfall Retreat",
      "role": "mobility",
      "canonical_element": "physical",
      "seasonal_element": null,
      "geometry_type": "dash_attack",
      "energy_cost": 12.1,
