          "name": "damage",
          "params": {
            "magnitude": 0,
            "element": "physical"
          }
        }
      ],
      "flavor_text": "The dwarf lunges aside as the ceiling gives way, riding the collapse draft like a current through flooded stone. Where they stood, nothing remains but the damp creep of settling dust."
    }
